  "html_size": 192559,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110169867425\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110169867425\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"3028548_9\"; font-size: 9pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"> \r\n</span><div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"3028548_9\"; font-size: 9pt;'>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">[남성역 이수한의원/중이염]</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 0, 124); font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">중이염 치료와증상</span></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">유아기 아이들에게 중이염은 흔하게 발생하는질환 중에 하나입니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">중이염은 어떤 한가지 원인이 아닌 다양한 복합적 작용으로 생기는데 중이에 염증이 발생한 이유가 큽니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;특히 고막보다 더 깊이 있는 '중이'는 \"이관-유스타키오관\"을 통해 코 안쪽과 연결되어 있고 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">이관은 수시로 열렸다 <span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">닫혔다를 반복하는데, </span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">감기, 비염 등 코 문제로 이관이&nbsp;막히게 되면 중이염으로 이어집니다</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_259/isuhani_1370875754488CxSnD_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B01.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"234\" height=\"217\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 234px; rheight: 217px;\" id=\"20130610_259/isuhani_1370875754488CxSnD_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B01.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6A2C4A1')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_259/isuhani_1370875754488CxSnD_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B01.PNG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">이관이 막히고 중이가 감염되거나 기능적 손상을 일으키는 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">대표적인 원인은 감기, 비염, 등이 있는데 감기가 장기간 지속되면 중이내에 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">세균이 침투해 감염을 일어키고 이관이 부어 급성중이염이 생겨나게 됩니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_244/isuhani_1370875758848HsNkH_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B02.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"243\" height=\"350\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 243px; rheight: 350px;\" id=\"20130610_244/isuhani_1370875758848HsNkH_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B02.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6A2C4A1')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_244/isuhani_1370875758848HsNkH_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B02.PNG?type=w3\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">급성중이염이 시작되면 어린 아이들은 심한 발열과 통증으로 계속해 이유없이 울거나 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">잠을 제대로 이루지 못합니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;귀는 단지 귀의 문제가 아닌 코와 갚이 관련된 만큼 코 건강에 신경써야 합니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">특히 <span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">콧물 때문에&nbsp;지속적으로&nbsp;강하게 코를 푸는&nbsp;행위는&nbsp;중이염의 원인이 됩니다</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_101/isuhani_1370875762912gjoSM_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B03.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"497\" height=\"306\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 497px; rheight: 306px;\" id=\"20130610_101/isuhani_1370875762912gjoSM_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B03.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6A2C4A1')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_101/isuhani_1370875762912gjoSM_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B03.PNG?type=w3\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">문제는 그뿐이 아닙니다. </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">급성중이염이 발전하여 삼출성중이염이나 만성중이염으로 진행하면 더 골치아픕니다.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">​</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">삼출성중이염은 중이에 물이 고이는&nbsp;겁니다.&nbsp;&nbsp;굽성중이염과 같은 격렬한 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">발열과 통증이 없기 때문에 부모들은 오히려 증상이 호전되는 과정으로 착각하기&nbsp; 쉽습니다. 그러나 빨리 호전되지 않고 악화와 완화를 반복하게 되고, 항생제 등 소아과 약을 계속해서 먹게 하는 주된 질병입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_123/isuhani_1370875766959gbyCr_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B04.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"167\" height=\"218\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 167px; rheight: 218px;\" id=\"20130610_123/isuhani_1370875766959gbyCr_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B04.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6A2C4A1')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_123/isuhani_1370875766959gbyCr_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B04.PNG?type=w3\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">한방치료는 중이염을 단지 귀에 생긴 염증의 문제로 생각하기 보다 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">귀와 관련된 기관들의 기능 손상 및 몸의 면역력저하 문제와 연관지어 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">치료의 초점을 맞춥니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">특히 염증을 발생하게 하는 비염 축농증 등과 같은 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">코 질환들을&nbsp;치료해야 중이염의 뿌리를 뽑을 수&nbsp;있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_118/isuhani_13708757711640U5k6_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B05.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"298\" height=\"150\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 298px; rheight: 150px;\" id=\"20130610_118/isuhani_13708757711640U5k6_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B05.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6A2C4A1')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130610_118/isuhani_13708757711640U5k6_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B05.PNG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">따라서 남성역 이수한의원에서는&nbsp; 아이의 상태를 체계적으로 살피고 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">귀나 코와 관련된 기관의 기능회복과 면역력 강화를 위한 맞춤&nbsp;치료를&nbsp;합니다.</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">한가지 더!</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">중이염에 오랫동안 시달린 어린이는 성장발육 이 부실한 경우가 많기 때문에 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">정상적인 성장이 잘 이뤄지는지 체크를 하고 문제가 있다면 치료를 함께 하는&nbsp; 것이 좋습니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><img width=\"461\" height=\"613\" class=\"_photoImage\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMjFfMTAy/MDAxNTEzODE4OTczMTQ4.uNG4FOWkHcVz7FSMEoIWDLr7WiCo1eSO6ahaYUtin7cg.aezD7AKP3yaXmV7URdrR6HKZHAXvb2m9DVTM-4ekfWUg.PNG.isuhani/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9A%A9_%EC%95%BD%EB%A0%A5.png\" style=\"border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; rwidth: 461px; rheight: 613.28px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMjFfMTAy/MDAxNTEzODE4OTczMTQ4.uNG4FOWkHcVz7FSMEoIWDLr7WiCo1eSO6ahaYUtin7cg.aezD7AKP3yaXmV7URdrR6HKZHAXvb2m9DVTM-4ekfWUg.PNG.isuhani/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9A%A9_%EC%95%BD%EB%A0%A5.png?type=w3\" /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><!-- Not Allowed Attribute Filtered ( sqeid=\"QE_1521765510702393\") --><img width=\"473\" height=\"237\" class=\"_photoImage\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMjFfNTcg/MDAxNTEzODE4OTczMzIz.K4wdJ3cJIRYp-TK0iEZCgJwy8c9FGrU8170vdxIUSfAg.uNdNKDVweYPIMrr5LT3O1ZbPSxCAPu30Oi131Po6adog.PNG.isuhani/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9A%A9_%EC%A7%84%EB%A3%8C%EC%8B%9C%EA%B0%84_-_%EB%82%98.png\" style=\"border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; rwidth: 473px; rheight: 237px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMjFfNTcg/MDAxNTEzODE4OTczMzIz.K4wdJ3cJIRYp-TK0iEZCgJwy8c9FGrU8170vdxIUSfAg.uNdNKDVweYPIMrr5LT3O1ZbPSxCAPu30Oi131Po6adog.PNG.isuhani/%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9A%A9_%EC%A7%84%EB%A3%8C%EC%8B%9C%EA%B0%84_-_%EB%82%98.png?type=w3\" /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">​</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">​</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODAzMjNfMjkw/MDAxNTIxNzY1NTA5MDA0.G36aimKU7W6hox6wtv3T41Ch5y7zml8d9FIZ7gkkOuQg.pjdSWlwdP6Vp77nDzlJB_-dj_YDAn6K-QKda86lXP3Ag.JPEG.isuhani/%EA%B2%BD%ED%9D%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%88%98%ED%95%9C%EC%9D%98%EC%9B%90Logo-%EC%9B%B9%EC%9A%A9_100k_%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%98.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"135\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 135px;\" id=\"MjAxODAzMjNfMjkw/MDAxNTIxNzY1NTA5MDA0.G36aimKU7W6hox6wtv3T41Ch5y7zml8d9FIZ7gkkOuQg.pjdSWlwdP6Vp77nDzlJB_-dj_YDAn6K-QKda86lXP3Ag.JPEG.isuhani/%EA%B2%BD%ED%9D%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%88%98%ED%95%9C%EC%9D%98%EC%9B%90Logo-%EC%9B%B9%EC%9A%A9_100k_%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%98.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6A2C4A1')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODAzMjNfMjkw/MDAxNTIxNzY1NTA5MDA0.G36aimKU7W6hox6wtv3T41Ch5y7zml8d9FIZ7gkkOuQg.pjdSWlwdP6Vp77nDzlJB_-dj_YDAn6K-QKda86lXP3Ag.JPEG.isuhani/%EA%B2%BD%ED%9D%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%88%98%ED%95%9C%EC%9D%98%EC%9B%90Logo-%EC%9B%B9%EC%9A%A9_100k_%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%98.jpg?type=w3\">​</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 162); font-family: 굴림,Gulim; font-size: 11pt;\"><br /></span></strong></p>\r\n</div></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
